Rating: 3
This recipe is so simple, yet so delicious! The only thing I did differently was to let the garlic sit in the oil and vinegar for about 1 hour before proceeding. This allowed the garlic to infuse into the mixture for a more "garlicky" taste. I would also recommend cutting the baguettes a little thinner and once toasted, cut them into three smaller pieces.

